name: Lake County Health Department
tweet: [2/2] Our vaccination sites will continue to provide 1st and 2nd doses. We remind residents that those with 1st and 2nd doses continue to be well protected from severe illness, hospitalization, and death from COVID-19. If you haven't gotten your vaccine, now is a great time.

name: Lake County Health Department
tweet: [1/2] Today, the @US_FDA authorized boosters of the Pfizer vaccine for those ages 65+ and those at high risk of severe COVID-19. The @CDCgov's ACIP will meet to provide recommendations, including clarification on who will be included in these groups.
